properties.headline: Gale Warning issued February 12 at 2:20AM CST until February 13 at 9:00AM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
...PERIOD OF GUSTY NORTH WINDS EXPECTED TONIGHT AND THURSDAY...
...GUSTY SOUTHWEST WINDS THIS AFTERNOON FOR THE NEARSHORE
WATERS...

* WHAT...North winds 20 to 30 kt with gusts up to 35 kt and
waves 6 to 11 feet expected.

* WHERE...Portions of Lake Michigan.

* WHEN...From 9 PM this evening to 9 AM CST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous waves which could
capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 9 PM THIS EVENING TO 9 AM CST THURSDAY
